 311, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999970735345489, \"rank\": 2.9264740766412233e-06, \"text\": \"ABC News\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Colin Kerr\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"An Olympic shooting gold medallist\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"his chance\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 387}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 425}, {\"ngram\": \"a New South Wales tribunal\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"his gun licence application\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Diamond, 51, had his Category A firearms licence revoked in 2018 after he wasfound guiltyof firearms and drink driving charges in Port Stephens in 2017.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_D\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2369876701503689e-20, \"text\": \"Michael Diamond\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_D\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_D\"}, {\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Stephens_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5285815167708993e-17, \"text\": \"Port Stephens\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Stephens_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Stephens_Council\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Category A firearms licence\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"guiltyof firearms\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"driving charges\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Diamond was acquitted of the three firearms charges on appeal later that year.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Diamond\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"the three firearms charges\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"appeal\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He challenged the licence ban but the appeal wasupheld in January last year.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the licence ban\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"the appeal\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In September, he sought an administrative review of a decision to refuse a new application for a gun licence.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"an administrative review\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"a new application\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"a gun licence\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That decision has been upheld by the NSW Civil and Administrative Tribunal, meaning he will not be able to take part in the upcoming national Olympic qualifiers.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales\", \"score\": 0.9296623847018276, \"rank\": 0.07565922910371396, \"text\": \"NSW\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That decision\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming national Olympic qualifiers\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 51-year-old had been a successful competitive sporting shooter since a young age and won two gold medals in the sport at the 1996 and 2000 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a successful competitive sporting shooter\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"two gold medals\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1996 and 2000 Olympics\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diamond tried to overturn the decision in time for the Australian National Titles.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9997974158774976, \"rank\": 0.00020240793034677915, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Diamond\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(ABC News: Karen Barlow) Diamond had told the tribunal he needed a firearms licence before January 16, 2024 to \\\"compete at the Australian National Titles, the first selection competition for the [Paris] Olympic Games\\\".\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1362, \"end\": 1367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_people\", \"score\": 0.9990334452413817, \"rank\": 0.0009549517840735727, \"text\": \"Karen\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Barlow\", \"score\": 0.9999976098485064, \"rank\": 2.390114552401147e-06, \"text\": \"Barlow\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Barlow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Barlow\"}, {\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9997974158774976, \"rank\": 0.00020240793034677915, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994334281623, \"rank\": 5.665722306214488e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tribunal\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"a firearms licence\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"the first selection competition\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diamond argued he could be trusted given the work he had put in to improve himself since the ban was imposed.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Diamond\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"the ban\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The judgement handed down on January 5 stated Diamond had undertaken therapy, a road intervention program and firearm safety training.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The judgement\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"Diamond\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"a road intervention program\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"firearm safety training\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow Olympian Russel Mark OAM gave a character reference and said he \\\"could not speak more highly of Michael as a competitor\\\".\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1847, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0149526592631344e-37, \"text\": \"OAM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a character reference\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"Michael\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitor\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He has only ever conducted himself with utmost respect and dignity,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"utmost respect\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"dignity\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the judgement, Diamond said he had lost more than $1 million in sponsorship and related income due to losing his licence.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the judgement\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"Diamond\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsorship and related income\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"his licence\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The NSW Police Force argued the programs and mentoring undertaken by Diamond did not amount to \\\"significant steps in demonstrating reformed behaviour\\\" due to the serious nature of his offending.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2169, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales_Police_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NSW Police Force\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales_Police_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales_Police_Force\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the programs\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"mentoring\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"Diamond\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"significant steps\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"reformed behaviour\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2314}, {\"ngram\": \"the serious nature\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"his offending\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tribunal ultimately found Diamond had not taken enough steps to improve his behaviour and that granting a firearms licence would not be in the public interest.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tribunal\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"Diamond\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2398}, {\"ngram\": \"enough steps\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2425}, {\"ngram\": \"his behaviour\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"a firearms licence\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"the public interest\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even if I were to accept genuine remorse and commitment to reformed behaviour, the tribunal cannot ignore the applicant's history,\\\" the judgement stated.\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"genuine remorse\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2567}, {\"ngram\": \"commitment\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"reformed behaviour\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"the tribunal\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"the applicant's history\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"the judgement\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The weight of that history is such that it cannot be overcome by a recent period of mentoring, counselling and training.\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The weight\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"that history\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"a recent period\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"mentoring\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"counselling\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Editor's note January 9, 2024: The article has been updated to clarify that Mr Diamond's firearms conviction was acquitted on appeal in 2017.\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Editor's note\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2818}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2826}, {\"ngram\": \"The article\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Diamond's firearms conviction\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2913}, {\"ngram\": \"appeal\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Topic:Powerlifting Topic:NRL Topic:Ashes Topic:Ashes Analysis by Dean Bilton Topic:Superannuation Analysis by Annabel Crabb Topic:Federal Government Topic:War Topic:Foreign Affairs Topic:Shooting Sports Topic:Crime Prevention Courts Nelson Bay Newcastle Olympic Games Shooting Sports Sport Topic:Superannuation Analysis by Annabel Crabb Topic:Federal Government Topic:War Topic:Foreign Affairs Topic:Media Industry Topic:Indigenous Policy Topic:Explainer Topic:Urban Development and Planning Your home of Australian stories, conversations and events that shape our nation.\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 3547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rugby_League\", \"score\": 0.606459107895361, \"rank\": 0.6489145621557941, \"text\": \"NRL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rugby_League\", \"dbped